  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK498">
<l>ciṟupaṭaiyāṉ celliṭañ cēri ṉuṟupaṭaiyā</l>
<l> ṉūkka maḻintu viṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The power of one who has a large army will perish, if he goes into ground where only a small army can act.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
